Package: zscorer
Type: Package
Title: Child Anthropometry z-Score Calculator
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mark", "Myatt", email = "mark@brixtonhealth.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Ernest", "Guevarra", email = "ernestgmd@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A tool for calculating z-scores and centiles for weight-for-age, 
    length/height-for-age, weight-for-length/height, BMI-for-age, 
    head circumference-for-age, age circumference-for-age, subscapular skinfold-for-age, 
    triceps skinfold-for-age based on the WHO Child Growth Standards. 
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: tidyr
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    shiny,
    shinythemes,
    covr
License: AGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/nutriverse/zscorer
BugReports: https://github.com/nutriverse/zscorer/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr

